name: ZilStream
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en: ZilStream is a dashboard and tracker for Zilliqa and ZRC-2 tokens. Listing realtime tokens prices and market data and allowing you to monitor your balances, liquidity pools, staking and more.
